      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about wanting to die, it's just about them. i look at their faces and i just see how much my struggle weighs on them. it feels almost selfish to keep dragging them through my chaos when they could just... be free of it if i wasn't around. like, wouldn't it be more of a gift to them if i just stopped being a burden?",
